{%- comment -%}
  Product Thumbnail
    Self explanitory, this is the thumbnail display of a product for use in any
    place where you want a small version of the product to display.

  Params:
    product - Product to print
    variant - Specific variant to print, otherwise just use the first available.
    collection - Collection this product belongs to if any.

  Version:
    1.0.0 - 2018/11/27
{%- endcomment -%}


{%- comment -%} Determine defaults {%- endcomment -%}
{%- unless variant != blank -%}
  {%- assign variant = product.selected_or_first_available_variant -%}
{%- endunless -%}

{%- if customer -%}
  {%- include 'object.product-thumbnail-collection' -%}
{%- else -%}
  {%- include 'object.product-thumbnail-logout' -%}
{%- endif -%}
